item.title: An Example Post
item.description: Prologue Just testing some markdown stuff to see how it works with Hugo. May delete this later, or may keep it as a reference. For the record, I write my Markdown in Obsidian so I get a bit of a WYSIWYG thing going on – I know the whole point of Markdown is that it’s supposed to be readable on its own, but hey – don’t judge me :) One of these days I’ll learn some HTML.
